last_episode_to_air.name: Pacific Palisades
last_episode_to_air.overview: Carol is a salon owner who is looking to relocate with her husband and expand her business to Southern California.  She's about to see three properties in Pacific Palisades where space for her grand kids is a must!

name: Million Dollar House Hunters
overview: Very few of us have a big budget to spend on a house. We meet the select few who have millions to invest in high-end Real Estate. Our host takes home buyers on a tour of three ritzy mansions, these house hunters are super rich and in search for the perfect luxury home.
